- day_slots
- nutrition_summary_paid_only
- pantry_hint_paid_only
- history_preview

### output_fields_exact
- day_header:
  - meal_date
  - weekday_label
  - budget_tier
- day_slots[]:
  - meal_slot_id
  - meal_category
  - menu_title
  - source_type
  - servings
