  - estimated_kcal
  - memo
  - actual_status
  - changed_flag
  - changed_reason
- history_preview[]:
  - meal_history_id
  - actual_result_type
  - actual_menu_name
  - note
  - recorded_at

### write_actions
- update_plan_slot
- record_meal_history
- export_csv

### api_binding
- GET /api/mealplanner/plan/detail
- POST /api/mealplanner/plan/slot/update
- POST /api/mealplanner/history/record
- POST /api/mealplanner/export/csv

### validation
