  - menu_master_id_or_reference_id
  - menu_title
  - source_type
  - estimated_cost
  - estimated_kcal
  - score_summary

### write_actions
- search_menu
- suggest_menu

### api_binding
- POST /api/mealplanner/menu/search
- POST /api/mealplanner/menu/suggest

### validation
- page >= 1
- page_size reasonable
- meal_category valid enum
- budget_tier valid enum

